Klasse
Beschreibung
App
The main entry point for the JavaFX Minesweeper application.
Cell
Represents a single cell in the Minesweeper game grid.
Controller
The base controller class that provides common functionality for other controllers in the Minesweeper application.
FileManager
The FileManager class handles file management for the Minesweeper application.
GameController
The GameController class manages the Minesweeper gameplay, including UI, game logic, sound effects, and interactions with other components like leaderboard management and user data.
Launcher
A simple launcher class to start the Minesweeper application.
LeaderboardClient
A client for interacting with the leaderboard server.
LeaderboardController
Controller class for managing the global leaderboard UI in the Minesweeper game.
MenuController
Controller class for managing the main menu UI in the Minesweeper game.
MusicPlayer
The MusicPlayer class is responsible for handling the playback of background music and sound effects.
UserData
Represents user data for the Minesweeper game, including username and best times for different difficulties.
UserDataManager
The UserDataManager class handles the saving and loading of user data for the Minesweeper game.
UsernameMenuController
Controller for the "Username Menu" of the Minesweeper application.
